          "scale": {
            "x": 1,
            "y": 1
          },
          "type": "TextBox",
          "size": 24,
          "text": "<font>Then, we can interpret the probability for s successes in n steps, as a probability for<br>being at a distance x, after time t, using equations (blah) and (bleh):<br></font>",
          "selected": false
        },
        {
